        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="安装Hexo教程"><a href="#安装Hexo教程" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo教程"></a>安装Hexo教程</h1><h2 id="一、安装nodejs"><a href="#一、安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="一、安装nodejs"></a>一、安装nodejs</h2><p>nodejs 下载链接：<a href="https://nodejs.org/download/release/latest-v13.x/">https://nodejs.org/download/release/latest-v13.x/</a></p><h2 id="二、安装git"><a href="#二、安装git" class="headerlink" title="二、安装git"></a>二、安装git</h2><p>git 下载链接：<a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads">https://git-scm.com/downloads</a></p><h2 id="三、终端运行命令安装Hexo"><a href="#三、终端运行命令安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="三、终端运行命令安装Hexo"></a>三、终端运行命令安装Hexo</h2><p>sudo npm install hexo-cli -g</p>]]></content>
      
      
